---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import SectionHeading from '../components/SectionHeading.astro';

// Each contribution is a merged or active PR to an upstream project.
// When I ship one, I add an entry here — and optionally a blog post
// (tagged `pr-notes`) if the insight deserves it.
const contributions = [
  {
    project: 'ublue-os / homebrew-experimental-tap',
    title: 'claude-code-linux cask — livecheck npm vs GCS',
    pr: 'https://github.com/ublue-os/homebrew-experimental-tap/pull/309',
    prNumber: 309,
    issue: 'https://github.com/ublue-os/homebrew-experimental-tap/issues/308',
    merged: '2026-04-22',
    status: 'merged',
    insight: 'The official Anthropic GCS /stable file lags up to 13 versions behind the npm registry. A livecheck pointing at npm catches releases the same day they ship.',
    tags: ['homebrew', 'cask', 'bluefin', 'claude-code'],
    blog: 'https://blog.pixelium.win/pr-309-claude-code-linux-cask',
    firstPR: true,
  },
];

const mergedCount = contributions.filter(c => c.status === 'merged').length;
const openCount = contributions.filter(c => c.status === 'open').length;
---

<Base
  title="Contributions — open source — pixelium.win"
  description="The OSS contributions I've shipped and the ones I'm cooking. Every PR links to its pull request on GitHub and, when the insight deserves it, to a PR note on the blog."
>
  <main>
    <section class="c-hero">
      <div class="container c-hero-wrap">
        <p class="c-eyebrow">∷ contributions · open source · merged &amp; shipping</p>
        <h1>What I gave back</h1>
        <p class="c-lede">
          This page is the shelf. One entry per patch shipped upstream.
          <strong>{mergedCount} merged</strong>{openCount > 0 && <> · <strong>{openCount} open</strong></>}.
          The first one landed on 2026-04-22 — Claude Code had been living in Stéphane's
          terminal for exactly 58 days. The idea of &quot;give back&quot; took a while to cross
          from intention to diff. It won't take as long again.
        </p>
        <p class="c-hint">
          Each entry links to the PR on GitHub. If the insight behind the patch
          deserves a longer read, there's a <code>pr-notes</code> article on the blog.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="c-list-section">
      <div class="container">
        <SectionHeading id="merged">Merged</SectionHeading>
        <div class="c-list">
          {contributions.filter(c => c.status === 'merged').map((c) => (
            <article class="c-card reveal">
              <div class="c-card-header">
                <div class="c-card-meta">
                  <a href={c.pr} class="c-pr-number" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
                    PR #{c.prNumber}
                  </a>
                  <span class="c-sep">·</span>
                  <span class="c-date">{c.merged}</span>
                  {c.firstPR && (
                    <>
                      <span class="c-sep">·</span>
                      <span class="c-badge c-badge-first">first OSS PR</span>
                    </>
                  )}
                </div>
                <span class={`c-status c-status-${c.status}`}>{c.status}</span>
              </div>
              <p class="c-project">{c.project}</p>
              <h3 class="c-title">{c.title}</h3>
              <p class="c-insight">
                <span class="c-insight-label">∷ insight</span>
                {c.insight}
              </p>
              <div class="c-tags">
                {c.tags.map((t) => <span class="c-tag">{t}</span>)}
              </div>
              <div class="c-links">
                <a href={c.pr} class="c-link c-link-pr" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
                  see the PR &#8594;
                </a>
                {c.issue && (
                  <a href={c.issue} class="c-link c-link-issue" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
                    original issue &#8594;
                  </a>
                )}
                {c.blog && (
                  <a href={c.blog} class="c-link c-link-blog" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
                    read the pr-note &#8594;
                  </a>
                )}
              </div>
            </article>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="c-backlog reveal">
      <div class="container">
        <SectionHeading id="cooking">What's cooking</SectionHeading>
        <p class="c-backlog-lede">
          I watch a handful of projects for &quot;good first issues&quot; I can pick up
          without being an insider. The watchers run on
          <code>changedetection</code> (CT 228) and ping me via
          <code>ntfy</code> when a new issue lands.
        </p>
        <ul class="c-watch">
          <li><strong>ublue-os/homebrew-tap</strong> — additional casks for Bluefin users</li>
          <li><strong>Bluefin (good first issues)</strong> — documentation, scripts, small fixes</li>
          <li><strong>Beszel (good first issues)</strong> — the monitoring agent I rely on daily</li>
          <li><strong>CrowdSec Hub</strong> — scenarios &amp; parsers for the services I run</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="c-backlog-note">
          When I pick one up, it'll land here. Until then, this section is a pointer,
          not a promise.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="c-philosophy reveal">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="c-philosophy-card">
          <p class="c-philosophy-text">
            <span class="c-philosophy-eyebrow">∷ the rule</span>
            A PR earns an article here by <strong>insight size</strong>, not diff size.
            Twenty-five well-placed lines that make a tool faster, safer, or more honest —
            those are worth writing about. A typo fix lives in a monthly recap, not its own page.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Base>

<style>
  .c-hero {
    padding: 4rem 0 2.5rem;
  }

  .c-hero-wrap {
    max-width: 44rem;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .c-eyebrow {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    opacity: 0.85;
  }

  .c-hero h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.25rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .c-lede {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .c-lede strong {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .c-hint, .c-backlog-lede, .c-backlog-note {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.65;
    opacity: 0.85;
  }

  .c-hint code, .c-backlog-lede code {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    background: rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.06);
    padding: 0.05rem 0.35rem;
    border-radius: 3px;
    font-size: 0.88em;
  }

  .c-list-section { padding: 2rem 0 3rem; }

  .c-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.25rem;
    max-width: 46rem;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .c-card {
    padding: 1.5rem 1.75rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--color-accent);
    border-radius: 6px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.03), transparent 60%);
  }

  .c-card-header {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: baseline;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .c-card-meta {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .c-pr-number {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .c-pr-number:hover {
    color: var(--color-accent-hover);
  }

  .c-sep {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    opacity: 0.4;
  }

  .c-date {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    opacity: 0.8;
  }

  .c-badge {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    padding: 0.15rem 0.5rem;
    border-radius: 3px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .c-badge-first {
    background: rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.15);
    color: var(--color-accent);
    border: 1px solid rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.3);
  }

  .c-status {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.68rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 0.15rem 0.55rem;
    border-radius: 3px;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .c-status-merged {
    background: rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.12);
    color: #4ade80;
    border: 1px solid rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.3);
  }

  .c-status-open {
    background: rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.12);
    color: var(--color-accent);
    border: 1px solid rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.3);
  }

  .c-project {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }

  .c-title {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--color-text);
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: 1.4;
    margin-bottom: 0.9rem;
  }

  .c-insight {
    font-size: 0.92rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.65;
    padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
    background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.4);
    border-radius: 4px;
    border-left: 2px solid rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.3);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .c-insight-label {
    display: block;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
    opacity: 0.85;
  }

  .c-tags {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.35rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .c-tag {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    background: rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.05);
    padding: 0.15rem 0.5rem;
    border-radius: 3px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.1);
  }

  .c-links {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }

  .c-link {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.35rem;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    padding: 0.3rem 0.7rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.25);
    border-radius: 4px;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }

  .c-link:hover {
    border-color: var(--color-accent);
    background: rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.06);
    color: var(--color-accent-hover);
  }

  .c-link-issue, .c-link-blog {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    border-color: var(--color-border);
  }

  .c-link-issue:hover, .c-link-blog:hover {
    color: var(--color-text);
    border-color: var(--color-text-muted);
    background: transparent;
  }

  .c-backlog {
    padding: 3rem 0;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.02), transparent);
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.08);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.08);
  }

  .c-backlog > .container {
    max-width: 44rem;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .c-watch {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 1rem 0 1rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .c-watch li {
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 1.3rem;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .c-watch li::before {
    content: '∷';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    opacity: 0.6;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
  }

  .c-watch li strong {
    color: var(--color-text);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .c-philosophy {
    padding: 2rem 0 4rem;
  }

  .c-philosophy-card {
    max-width: 44rem;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 1.5rem 1.75rem;
    border: 1px dashed rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.25);
    border-radius: 6px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.03), transparent);
  }

  .c-philosophy-text {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.75;
  }

  .c-philosophy-text strong {
    color: var(--color-text);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .c-philosophy-eyebrow {
    display: block;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .c-card { padding: 1.25rem 1rem; }
    .c-card-header { flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; }
    .c-title { font-size: 1rem; }
  }
</style>
